title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - What's new in the marketplace - week 12
description:
In this video we will look at the latest additions to the MSFS 2020 marketplace this week. This week besides a lot of flight plans which makes it possible to simulate if you are a real pilot for multiple airliners a bunch of new airports and a new fighter jet are added. Additionally if you want to refuel your fighters in the air Captain Sim also released a nice present for you.
